	<h1>Stanford: Limerick</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p class="dateline">February 7</p>

<p>Kat interrupts me from updating this blog and writes a limerick:</p>

<p>There once was a boy named Aaron <br />
Who studies stuff like file sharin&#8217; <br />
Though his days were fraught <br />
With lots o&#8217; intense thought <br />
The sight of a Skittle would scare &#8216;im</p>

<p>I make more verbal errors around Kat than everyone else combined.</p>

<p class="dateline">February 8</p>

<p>I use the phrase &#8220;My friend and I were actually discussing this last night&#8221; three times today, with reference to at least two different people, which implies I have at least some friends.</p>

<p class="posted">posted February 27, 2005 01:56 AM (<a class="category" href="http://www.aaronsw.com/weblog/cat_education">Education</a>) (<a href="001594#comments">2 comments</a>) <a href="001594" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

